Pegasus Intellectual Capital Solutions is a leading boutique middle market investment bank and management consulting firm serving business owners related to mergers and acquisitions; capital raising; exit planning; restructuring; and management consulting. We are former portfolio managers that understand companies with unique insight, and see value in companies that is unseen by others. Our industries include Agribusiness/Ag Tech, Business Services, Distribution, Extractive Energy, Food & Beverage, Healthcare, Manufacturing, and Technology.




 


